Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖觀音的手所指之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.38,0:01:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將前往\N大富士的山麓之道打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那條路非常險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通往地獄深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.13,0:02:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第八十六話\N地底的紅色蒸氣  殺鬼！真田三人眾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地獄深淵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一句顯得有點平凡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用廢話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像神話中出現的神殿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.21,0:02:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是東方人的猴戲罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 修奈特少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是鐘乳石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是漫長歲月當中\N貼下木造的表面的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是木造\N怎麼看都不像是日本建築
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真的是\N御沙薙祖先製造的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照我們的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.14,0:03:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠在興盛強大的\N大和勢力融合之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.11,0:03:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古代諏訪有獨自繁榮的文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是真田的祖先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 猴子智慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.65,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟想拿祖先\N留下的靈藥得到日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.85,0:03:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這隻小猴子還挺有智慧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若愛惜生命\N就把這只骯髒的手拿開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御沙薙 這些人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.70,0:03:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔任我的貼身護衛\N的真田三人眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來試試他們有多大本領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷茲少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.61,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是來這裏戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你沒露出這無禮態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也不會出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說無禮！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,騎士的座右銘是\N勇氣、禮節、名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對女性的禮節\N應該沒有德國日本之分的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.23,0:04:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照我們的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.27,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該對女性表示敬意\N請她先走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來 女士優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操 阿薰 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.43,0:04:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們到底怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 可是照這樣下去\N可能會步上前人的後塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前人？這麼說這下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別在這地方變成鬼出現\N拜託啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.99,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到黑騎士團\N會跟真田忍者群聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又沒拜託你過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你不做好調查\N就進來事情才變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.73,0:05:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個西洋鬼子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是石頭腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 石頭腦袋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看看自己\N是坐在誰的身上打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 這時候還打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之平安無事就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總不能眼睜睜\N讓他們得到寶物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快離開這裏吧 好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這個臭味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏一片漆黑怎麼尋找出口呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你們以為\N自己跟誰在一起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 忍者有這點東西\N是小常識啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我馬上點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是御庭番眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.45,0:06:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可靠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是硫磺的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 如劍心所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地上有屍體的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.29,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硫磺與磷份混合起來\N等於是天然的火柴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏點火會大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點程度對人體健康應該沒有大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.67,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 火山活動頻繁的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會大量噴出瓦斯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間聽你慢慢分析了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去不需多久\N大家都上西天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 快想辦法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對學問沒研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好強烈的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 沒路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無處可退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想在這地方變成死人骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 快想辦法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然平日你吃那麼多飯\N是幹嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格說我我要是有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就做了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算避免窒息而死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下水脈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個牆壁的另一邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有地下水流經的水路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要順水流而走\N說不定可以出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管三七二十一了\N左之助 該你上場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 只要打破牆壁就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.01,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是第一次進來\N不可能知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.93,0:08:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有微妙差別\N但是真的太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.54,0:08:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是真田忍者群傳下來的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了我們以外應該沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是湊巧偶然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.21,0:09:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修奈特 除了徽章以外\N沒別的線索嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.22,0:09:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有的被磨滅了看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.42,0:09:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刻在這上面的文字\N也很酷似西方的古代文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾達斯中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.23,0:09:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也有同樣的東西\N這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來都是置在分歧點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是祖先留下來的路標嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.78,0:09:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 看到這個\N我不禁想起我族流傳的神話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說我們的祖先之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.55,0:09:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一支\N成為海上之民向東渡海而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.29,0:09:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定御沙薙你們的祖先…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我們祖先\N在很久以前是有關聯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是在想這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常有人這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 走吧 天就快要亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝到水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看大家這是什麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們下來的方式\N就不能好看一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒那個閒暇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.13,0:10:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候\N我們還是輸給學過忍術的人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 有個人倒在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地方會有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家全把我給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊 由太郎正在照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真田的忍者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是傷勢很重\N這樣下去的話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 你還不可以動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你受重傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.90,0:11:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好歹也是忍者\N不會輕易死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得非常不解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏應該是\N真田忍者群的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是被誰殺傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒必要告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼不打過來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你們拖下去墊我的棺材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管發生什麼事\N難得撿回一條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒必要浪費它呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不攻過來我就攻過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又昏過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需立刻動手術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手術？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要試試看請大家協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了我能幫多少就幫多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是全部的道具了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛鏢可以當手術使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有針跟線 這就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水煮沸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尋找岩石凹進去的地方\N把湯倒進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別搖 要是潑到怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎你想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消毒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.18,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能在不衛生的狀態下\N碰觸他的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 那是熱水耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會被燙傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 快把手拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你閉嘴 這是為了拯救患者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.06,0:12:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,患者他是敵人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對醫生而言 他是病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在醫學面前\N沒有敵人與自己人之分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.64,0:12:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡力拯救受傷與生病的人\N這就是醫生的戰鬥呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能得救嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷口縫好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是模仿博士罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在\N我是衷心希望他可以救活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎 你很了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道西醫的偉大之處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.45,0:13:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大家 好了 出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得再次回去那裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能把\N神聖的靈藥交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可能來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做手術時我瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神聖的靈藥\N是醫學發展時所需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不能成為\N他們達成野心的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 你還不能動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫由太郎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.55,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶我去 我知道秘道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是真田的戒太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.46,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不會再被准許\N使用真田這名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們別被騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可能是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假裝被自己人背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來背後捅我們一刀\N我可受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我瞭解你懷疑的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在事態刻不容緩\N所以還是帶我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.25,0:14:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走這條路 可以直接到達\N你們摔下來的那地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.82,0:14:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 放心吧 我只是晃了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真的可以信任那男人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你在擔心 可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何不姑且相信戒太看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他當爛好人的習慣\N又不是現在才養成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.66,0:15:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 從這裏直接下去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走 一次一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要盡量安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 紅色頭髮的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.79,0:15:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煉、斬 你們跟漠一起去迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御沙薙 這些蝙蝠是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.57,0:16:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍者的使魔是不限於人類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿動物當僕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然適合野蠻的東洋猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.58,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些蝙蝠幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漠的蝙蝠脾氣很壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,激怒他們會討皮肉痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了 你們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才說的話我取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們看起來挺可愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.04,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些蝙蝠是頭一次\N親近我跟漠以外的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 我也可以當忍者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不知道了\N忍者的修行很嚴苛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請你手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御沙薙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才聽你提到\N紅色頭髮的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且帶路的人是戒太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能 戒太是我殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道為什麼\N他們倆都還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且使用我們的秘道\N來到附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他們還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個紅色頭髮的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個小嘍嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來一次 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 讓我來助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 這地方地面不平\N你的竹刀劍術沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是忍者耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是左之助之前不是說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由太郎用醫術救人\N你就以劍來救人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你該分清楚時機跟場合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.24,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥他是被由太郎的行為\N打動心靈了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.35,0:18:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥 雖然有點危險\N你願接下這工作嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在看哪裏 這邊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他竟然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.23,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是小鬼\N我是神谷活心流的明神彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧 我當你們對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要讓你再也不敢說大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.69,0:18:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以站起來吧\N你演得很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少嘍唆 不用繞彎來嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有嘲笑你\N剛才真的很神氣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.32,0:19:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼西洋的街道會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.66,0:19:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是博士所說的遺跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哪個笨蛋\N玩弄這種危險玩具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又出現一個瘋子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒有獵物了\N我們就玩到過癮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 別大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是真田三人眾的兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個是獵頭者「斬」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.27,0:20:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及大蛇「煉」\N不是你能對付的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看不起人了 我可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼呀 這些蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是躲在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田三人眾最後一人\N暗使者「漠」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去 真是禍不單行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想跟那武士交手一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是幕末時期\N被稱為傳說中的斬人劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊\N這就是他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊\N傳說中的斬人劍客嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.08,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我越來越想跟他交手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾 那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.79,0:20:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真田三人眾\N大概已經殺死他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修奈特\N你在做什麼 還不快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.90,0:20:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.93,0:21:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對他不會這麼有興趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心 這些是吸血蝙蝠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傷害少女的皮膚啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛的耶 呆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你閃邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.24,0:21:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輕易就放手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.59,0:21:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.99,0:22:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的鞭子讓人無法預測動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.23,0:22:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的功夫名不虛傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你有辦法\N進入我的鞭子攻擊範圍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能靠近的話只有一個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二連大蛇 地奔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土龍閃沒效！？

